Notes.Text:
This update for libqt5-qtbase fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2023-37369: Fixed buffer overflow in QXmlStreamReader (bsc#1214327).

- libq5-qtbase was rebuild against icu 73. jsc#PED-6193

Vulnerabilities.Description: In Qt before 5.15.15, 6.x before 6.2.9, and 6.3.x through 6.5.x before 6.5.2, there can be an application crash in QXmlStreamReader via a crafted XML string that triggers a situation in which a prefix is greater than a length.
